egory:Discographies of South Korean artists]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox artist discography\n| Artist        = Chungha\n| Image         = 170607 \uae40\uccad\ud558 \ub370\ubdd4 \uc1fc\ucf00\uc774\uc2a4 12 pic (3).jpg\n| Caption       = Chungha performing in 2017\n| 1Option       = 2\n| 1Option name  = Single albums\n| EP            = 4\n| Music videos  = 20\n| Singles       = 7\n| 2Option       = 7\n| 2Option name  = Collaborations\n| 3Option       = 8\n| 3Option name  = Soundtrack appearances\n}}\n\nThe discography of South Korean singer, dancer and rapper [[Chungha]] consists of four [[extended play]]s (EPs), seven singles, and twenty music videos. In addition, the singer has [[Collaboration|collaborative]] and [[soundtrack]]s for television series.\n\n==Albums==\n===Single albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of single albums, with selected chart positions and sales\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:8em;\" |Title\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"|Album details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\" | Peak chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\" |Sales\n|-\n! style=\"width:2.5em;\" |[[Gaon Chart|KOR]]</small><br><ref>Peak Gaon Chart Album Chart Ranking\n*{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=01&hitYear=2019&termGbn=week|title=XII|date=December  20, 2018 \u2013 January 5, 2019|website=Gaon Music Chart|language=ko|access-date=March 26, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=row|''[[Gotta Go (Chungha song)|XII]]''\n|\n* Released: January 2, 2019\n* Label: MNH Entertainment\n* Formats: [[Compact disc|CD]], [[Music download|digital download]]\n{{hidden|Track listing|\n#\"\ubc8c\uc368 12\uc2dc (Gotta Go)\"\n}}\n| 4\n| \n*KOR: 10,000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=01&hitYear=2019&termGbn=month|title=2019\ub144 01\uc6d4 Album Chart|website=Gaon Music 